
Fist build with AUTOTOOLS....

Starting files for this folder are 

sqroot.cpp (our simple c++ program)
configure.ac (our Autotools config file)
Makefile.am (our Makefile input for Automake).
and This README. Can erase all the other files.

In orderto use Autotools do the following:

autoreconf -i 	<--- this will generate the configure file
./configure     <--- this will generate the Makefile
make 		<--- this will build the source code
/sqroot_n 9	<--- this will run the program 

